snippet.title: TGS2024：First Peek into the Vehicle System | Dyson Sphere Program
snippet.description:
Greetings, fellow engineers. Great to see you again at TGS2024.
We are happy to bring you the preview of the Vehicle System. 
And some other future plans: 
-More Transport, Combat and QOL updates.
-Crossovers with other titles.
-More localizations supports: German, French, Japanese...
We're looking forward to the future contents that will bring more fun to our players. Stay tuned!
